quran[12{c,v,t}:
25,21,"jo log hamaray huzoor paish honay ka andesha nahi rakhtay woh kehte hain"" kyun nah farishtay hamaray paas beje jayen? ya phir hum apne rab ko dekhen"" bara ghamand le baithy yeh apne nafs mein aur hadd se guzar gay yeh apni sar kashi mein"
25,22,"jis roz yeh firshton ko dekhen ge woh mujrimon ke liye kisi basharat ka din nah hoga, cheekh utheen ge ke panah ba khuda"
25,23,aur jo kuch bhi un ka kya dhara hai ussay le kar hum gubhar ki terhan ura den ge
25,24,bas wohi log jo jannat ke mustahiq hain uss din achi jagah tehrayge aur dopehr guzarnay ko umdah maqam payen ge
25,25,aasman ko cheerta howa aik baadal is roz namodaar ho ga aur firshton ke paray ke paray utaar diye jayen ge
25,26,uss roz haqeeqi badshahi sirf Rehman ki ho gi aur woh munkareen ke liye bara sakht din ho ga
25,27,"zalim ensaan apna haath chuba-ay ga aur kahe ga"" kash mein ne rasool ka sath diya hota"
25,28,"haae meri kam bakhti, kash mein ne falan shakhs ko dost nah banaya hota"
25,29,"uss ke b_hkaye mein aa kar mein ne woh nasiyaat nah maani jo mere paas aayi thi, shetan ensaan ke haq mein bara hi be wafa nikla """
25,30,"aur rasool kahe ga ke"" ae mere rab, meri qoum ke logon ne is quran ko nishana tazheek bana liya tha """
25,31,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne to isi terhan mujrimon ko har nabi ka dushman banaya hai aur tumahray liye tumhara rab hi rahnumai aur madad ko kaafi hai"
25,32,"munkareen kehte hain"" iss shakhs par sara quran aik hi waqt mein kyun nah utaar diya gaya ?"" haan, aisa is liye kya gaya hai ke is ko achi terhan hum tumahray zehan nasheen karte rahen aur ( isi gharz ke liye ) hum ne is ko aik khaas tarteeb ke sath allag allag ajzaa ki shakal di hai"
